    "description": "<blockquote><p><strong>Requirements:</strong> You must have Mastered the <strong>Celebrity</strong> Class, and must have learned the <strong>Cultural Phenomenon</strong> skill.</p></blockquote><p>You have command over large groups of people in a way that often defies reason. When you speak, heads turn. Outside of a <strong>Conflict</strong>, you may spend 3 <strong>Reputation Point</strong> and choose a crowd of non-hostile humanoid creatures able to hear and understand you. If you do, those creatures become swayed by your voice, and against even their better judgement will follow your commands for the remainder of the scene. This effect also ends when the crowd disperses and for each individual when they leave the crowd.</p>",
